# Test Playwright Wait Methods

Test different ways to wait/pause in Playwright

## Keywords
test, wait, pause, delay

---

## Test 1: Navigate
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_navigate",
  "params": {
    "url": "https://example.com"
  }
}
```

## Test 2: Try page.waitForTimeout (if available)
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_evaluate",
  "params": {
    "script": "async () => { console.log('Starting 10 second wait...'); await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 10000)); console.log('Wait complete!'); return 'Waited 10 seconds'; }"
  }
}
```

